item.title: NFC business card
item.author: ulf.e.sv@gmail.com (Ulfsv)
item.description: Custom NFC business card Order your custom made business card. The NFC tag can be linked to a vcard, home page, youtube, facebook page or any kind of URL. Send us your design in pdf, svg or postscript or other vector graphic formats. Use high resolution images: 96 DPI or higher. Send us dropbox link if image size is larger than 10 Mb. The link on the NFC tag can easily be changed online.
